snippet.title: Mads Mikkelsen Makes Statement on Johnny Depp & Amber Heard | Throwing Johnny Under the Bus??
snippet.description:
Should Mads Mikkelsen have to pick a side in the Johnny Depp and Amber Heard controversy? He will be replacing Johnny Depp in the new Fantastic Beast by Warner Brothers and has some statements that we are going to go over. Let me know what you think!
